{"author":{"id":"b65f3d7cc6365cdda97889669465cb80d6eb6b487ba87271045738f4aaeb081b"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1585323467,"nonce":"0EoeIzQi35fN7qPnZ5hduKR+OlA=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDYwNTA2NzA5Mw==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/1707#issuecomment-605067093"},"message":"The latest binary version of tbl2asn needs `GLIBC_2.14` \nSo I had to compile from sources (`GLIBC_2.14` works fine for tbl2asn but breaks the other tools...)\n\n```\nwget https://ftp.ncbi.nih.gov/toolbox/ncbi_tools/CURRENT/ncbi.tar.gz\ntar -xvf ncbi.tar.gz\ncd ncbi/build\ngcc -pipe -D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64 -D_LARGEFILE64_SOURCE -D_GNU_SOURCE -g -o  tbl2asn -O3 -I../include  -L../lib tbl2asn.c  -lncbiid1 -lnetcli -lncbiobj -lconnssl -lncbi -lgnutls -lm -lncbitool\n```\nI'm not sure if all options are mandatory (I grab the command line from the build process and add -lm / -lncbitool)","files":null}]}